<h1>Gaining Posession</h1>
<li><h3><i>Circular Chasing</h3></i></li>
<table border="1"><tr><td>
<p>Mark out a circle with cones and spread players evenly around the circle</p>
<p>On the whistle players move around the circle while balancing the sliotar on the hurl</p>
<p>Players are attempting to catch the player directly in front of them while trying not to get caught by the player behind them.</p>
</table></tr></td>
