<li><h3><i>Change Of Direction</h3></i></li>
<table border="1"><tr><td>
<p>4 players per group working with 2 sliotars.</p>
<p>There is a square made up of four different coloured cones.</p>
<p>Player 1 solos quickly into the center of the square.</p>
<p>Player 2 calls a colour just as player 1 reaches the centre of the square.</p>
<p>Player 1 must change direction and move quickly to the assigned cone.</p>
<p>Player 2 repeats with player 3 calling the colour, etc..</p>
</table></tr></td>
